  <description><![CDATA[<h2>A multi-centre holiday to Alpbach and Pertisau combines rustic charm and green rolling hills with dramatic limestone peaks and the dazzling Lake Achensee</h2>
<p>Get a glimpse of authentic Austria on multi-centre holiday to Alpbach and Pertisau. Alpbach was once voted Austria's prettiest village and it's easy to see why - the small village is full of rustic buildings and flower-filled balconies, surrounding by green rolling hills, meadows and distant mountain peaks with plenty of walking trails to explore. Pertisau has an equally beautiful but contrasting setting, on a gentle plain between the bright waters of Lake Achensee and the dramatic limestone peaks of the Karwendel mountains. Here, there's every flavour of footpath from lakeside strolls to challenging summits. Or, hit the relax button and take a leisurely afternoon cruise.</p>
<h3>Guide price from: £pp*</h3>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options: </h3>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li>Travel and change destination on a Wednesday or Saturday</li>
<li>Combine stays of 3, 4, 7, 10 or 11 nights into a total holiday duration of 7, 10, 11 or 14 nights</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK</li>
<li>Transfers from the airport to your hotel in Alpbach, from your hotel in Alpbach to your hotel in Pertisau and from your hotel in Pertisau to the airport</li>
<li>Accommodation in your chosen hotel in each destination</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<p> </p>
