  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Alpbach</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/7e43ab133b364827985c5c801c1617c0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7e43ab133b364827985c5c801c1617c0}" title="Hotel Böglerhof">Hotel Böglerhof</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 300px; height: 200px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13109470/hotel_boglerhof_alpbach_pure_nature_adults_only_outdoor_pool.jpg?width=300&amp;height=200" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/73ccb018800640deb34630e7a788a9cb" />If you're looking for wow-factor then look no further than the five-star Hotel Böglerhof in Alpbach. It perfectly blends rustic charm with modern style and convenience, and has luxurious wellness facilities with both adult-only and family-friendly zones. When you add the first-class service and excellent food, you have everything you need for a luxurious stay in one of Austria's most beautiful villages.</p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/07fec0ae0d27493fbac2ae579230896c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07fec0ae0d27493fbac2ae579230896c}" title="Spa Resort Alpbacherhof">Spa Resort Alpbacherhof</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 300px; height: 200px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13109471/hotel_alpacherhof_alpbach_swimming_pool.jpg?width=300&amp;height=200" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/bdc3bc91b5104e72aff0eef0627b2d74" /></p>
<p>This hotel is one of Alpbach's most popular, with guests returning year on year. It's no surprise, with the uninterrupted views of the stunning Alpbach Valley from its south-facing gardens. It also has a 1,600-square-metre spa area and an interconnected indoor/outdoor pool, perfect for relaxing. </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d3da7b34473447c58a08fb31b2c5a7f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d3da7b34473447c58a08fb31b2c5a7f4}" title="Alpbach" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Hotels in Alpbach</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></facilityDescription>
