<p><img style="width: 300px; height: 200px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13109472/hotel_das_pfandler_pertisau_exterior.jpg?width=300&amp;height=200" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/fd514f88204542579876dfd88b603326" />Ideally located in the centre of Pertisau, the Hotel Das Pfandler is everything you need for a comfortable and convenient stay, with excellent food and service. There's an indoor pool and spa, perfect for post-hike relaxation and the garden is peaceful, with plenty of space for dozing in the sunshine or shade.</p>
