  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>A multi-centre holiday lets you mix and match hotels, lengths of stay, and exciting activities to create your ideal trip. Enjoy everything from panoramic walks, cultural tours and outdoor adventures to relaxing days and tasty local cuisine.</p>
<h3>Visit the traditional and rustic village of Alpbach</h3>
<p>Alpbach is surrounded by meadows, forests and the Gratlspitz peaks - it's a village from the pages of a fairy tale. Wooden houses with flower-filled balconies decorate peaceful streets, while many of the surrounding farms have been run by the same families for centuries. It's one of the best places for digging into mountain food – just the fuel you need for hiking some of the valley's beautiful trails.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d3da7b34473447c58a08fb31b2c5a7f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d3da7b34473447c58a08fb31b2c5a7f4}" title="Alpbach" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About Alpbach</a></p>
<h3>Explore the Karwendel mountains and Lake Achensee from Pertisau</h3>
<p>Pertisau sits on the edge on Lake Achensee - the Tyrol's largest lake - at the eastern edge of the Karwendel mountain range. Take leisurely strolls along the lakeside, hop on a cruise or take the Karwendel lift high into the mountains. There are plenty of walking trails to explore and activities from lake sports to paragliding.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b5e429a18c1341518ff1c75889b2f4ea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b5e429a18c1341518ff1c75889b2f4ea}" title="Pertisau" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About Pertisau</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><em>Please note: This is an independent multi-centre holiday and you are free to choose your own itinerary in each destination. The above contains recommendations which are provided for information only and are not included in the price of your holiday. An Inghams Destination Expert will be on hand locally either in resort or by telephone and will provide advice and offer optional excursions and walking passes.</em></p>
<p><em>Special diets, including vegetarian, must be requested prior to booking.</em></p>
<p><em>The itineraries may be subject to change. Where this becomes necessary, and where practicable, we will take the steps as outlined in clause 5 of our <a data-udi="umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">terms and conditions</a>.</em></p>]]></locationDescription>
